{"tid":1669981,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇美斯月薪多過巴塞一年賺既錢","createTime":"2019-10-23T00:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T11:09:29.000Z","uid":34293,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1c9e6f3b178593c6fabbd3e0459f32b24356b500","tid":1669981,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T00:19:47.000Z","msg":"7月26日訊 巴薩董事會已經決定關閉俱樂部2018/19賽季的賬戶。這賽季的賬戶最終顯示俱樂部年收入達到了創紀錄的9.9億歐元（11.04億美元），同時年支出達到9.73億歐元（10.85億美元）。營業利潤達到1700萬歐（1990萬美元），稅後凈利潤達到450萬歐元（500萬美元）。息稅折舊攤銷前利潤為1.79億歐元（1.99億美元），因此負債率遠低於俱樂部章程第67條的規定水平。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我好驚有金融風暴搞到巴塞執笠"},{"pid":"d5786dd54f8ae6d7ba1da840abfc9d4b5ceab43b","tid":1669981,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T00:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3b34bbd59585a2fc5a0b2e674afe21b4c47f8c","tid":1669981,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861236a19450aa0dae22f66cd4a03525dd83c254","tid":1669981,"uid":36372,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:29:24.000Z","msg":"比埋人工都仲有咁多錢賺西利"},{"pid":"bffd0e4f7c99566cbd5baf348abe59ffb663ad38","tid":1669981,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"861236a19450aa0dae22f66cd4a03525dd83c254","tid":1669981,"uid":36372,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:29:24.000Z","msg":"比埋人工都仲有咁多錢賺西利"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:39:32.000Z","msg":"ynwa"},{"pid":"2c657451fbfc91b0ba58e5f0bf8b6c71ad6a5d50","tid":1669981,"uid":186292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:46:03.000Z","msg":"美斯踢多幾年都退休<br />\n到時就無咩邊個要比咁高人工"},{"pid":"07181ade7aadc1577dc256fc9617dcc3f4742ac8","tid":1669981,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c657451fbfc91b0ba58e5f